channel.title: Product Qualified online conference
channel.description:
On Thursday and Friday (Nov 14 and 15 2019) the Product Qualified Conference takes place online. Basically the conference let's product marketing companies show what they can do. The schedule is here: https://productqualified.growthsandwich.com/schedule/ . You can register for free before November 16th, 2019.
@SteveMcLeod might be interesting if that kind of marketing (i.e. speaking or letting someone else speak) would help you?
